---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Automancer Ltd. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="page-hero hatch">
    <div class="page-hero__glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section on-dark">
    <div class="wrap wrap--text prose" style="margin-inline:auto">
      <h2>Controller</h2>
      <p>
        Automancer Ltd (company no. 17060907)<br />
        62 Beckfield Road, Bingley, BD16 1QS<br />
        Contact: <a href="mailto:waseem@automancer.uk">waseem@automancer.uk</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Data we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact details (name, email, company)</li>
        <li>Enquiry/project information you share</li>
        <li>Basic website analytics/cookie data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why we process data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to enquiries</li>
        <li>Deliver services</li>
        <li>Manage contracts/invoicing</li>
        <li>Improve website and services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Legal bases</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contract</li>
        <li>Legitimate interests</li>
        <li>Legal obligation</li>
        <li>Consent (where required)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We share data only where needed with trusted service providers (e.g., email, hosting,
        accounting), under appropriate safeguards.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We keep data only as long as needed for service delivery, legal obligations, and
        legitimate business records.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access, correction, deletion, restriction, objection, or portability
        where applicable.
      </p>
      <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:waseem@automancer.uk">waseem@automancer.uk</a></p>

      <h2>Sensitive/regulated work</h2>
      <p>
        Automancer excludes certain high-risk engagements (e.g., patient-data-heavy and
        government/military highly confidential systems) unless explicitly agreed.
      </p>

      <h2>Complaints</h2>
      <p>You can complain to the UK ICO if you believe your data rights were breached.</p>

      <h2>Updates</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
